<id>http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=237&amp;p=251#p251</id>
<link href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=237&amp;p=251#p251"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Royal English Club actitivities • 2018 Royal club year-end party &amp; installation]]></title>

<category term="Royal English Club actitivities" scheme="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewforum.php?f=9" label="Royal English Club actitivities"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=237&amp;p=251#p251"><![CDATA[
(12/8) 21 people, including senior members and new  friends, participated in  Royal club year end party &amp; installation.<br />1.we  enjoyed delicious food and sang interesting songs together in 星聚點.  We found many talented singers in our club. <br />2.We had a ceremony to  appreciate the devotion of  Presidents Jason Tang &amp; Shuman ,P.R. teams to the club in 2018. We also introduced and welcomed the 2019 team led by Morris &amp; Danny Lin. It is important to have volunteers to continue to support and manage this club.<br />3.Every participant made an impressive English speech.  We all agreed English is very  important, so we appreciated the funder, William, established this club 19 years ago,  making us have a good platform to practice English, enrich our knowledge, and meet friends.  We all sincerely hoped this club can last forever.<br />In conclusion, we had a wonderful and unforgettable party, so most of us will keep attending the regular meetings, and looked forward to next outing.<br />[img][/<div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/download/file.php?id=28" class="postimage" alt="2018.12.08PARTY_181210_0090.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div>img]<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Mon Dec 10, 2018 9:45 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
